                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, B</hi> 105). I assisted in examining the prisoner at the station—I saw he had something in his left hand—I took his hand and took three shillings from it, and another officer took one shilling—these are them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18510512-name-66" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18510512-name-66" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
