                        <interp inst="t18510512-name-66" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of coin to the Royal Mint—this shilling which was uttered is bad, and two of these other shillings are from the same mould—the other two are from the same mould—they are all bad.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had been drinking; I had no knowledge that they were bad; I work hard for my living.</p>
